{"tid":997822,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"真的解散「台上放聲大哭」　姜丹尼爾哭到跪下：沒有Wanna One了","createTime":"2019-01-27T12:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T06:13:02.000Z","uid":74065,"like":54,"dislike":177,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"72b4bfb743e48dacace4cdec2224d58ac5b70637","tid":997822,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T12:57:14.000Z","msg":"南韓人氣男團Wanna One從《PRODUCE 101 第二季》出道，歷經1年半的限定時間，他們27日舉辦最後一場「解散演唱會」，11人在唱到《12顆星星》時，忍不住在台上放聲大哭，姜丹尼爾掛著淚表示「不知道該說些什麼安慰大家，就只是覺得抱歉，很抱歉。」2萬名粉絲跟著哭出來，演唱會一片感傷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3866/d3866657.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3866%2Fd3866657.jpg&h=3ba674d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Wanna One於27日解散。（圖／翻攝自ollenTV）<br />\n<br />\nWanna One於27日在首爾舉辦解散演唱會，11名成員來自不同經紀公司，必定會面臨分別的一天，朴佑鎮淚喊：「如果一開始就知道結束會這麼難過的話，那為何要開始？」李大輝也感性表示「剛出道時曾覺得很痛苦，不知道這種日子還要過多久，但現在懊悔，覺得當時的想法很笨。」他們在唱到《12顆星星》時，看著台下坐滿2萬名觀眾，他們放聲大哭，哽咽唱完歌曲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3866/d3866659.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3866%2Fd3866659.jpg&h=2e2c66e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3866/d3866655.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3866%2Fd3866655.jpg&h=798373af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3866/d3866654.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3866%2Fd3866654.jpg&h=b5297331&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3866/d3866656.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3866%2Fd3866656.jpg&h=f70c744c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3866/d3866660.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3866%2Fd3866660.jpg&h=08ee410e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Wanna One成員一個一個哭慘。（圖／翻攝自ollenTV）<br />\n<br />\n姜丹尼爾哭到背對螢幕、一度跪在台上，他哽咽表示「在這裡遇到這10人，我真的很幸福，以後應該也會幸福，可是，Wanna One沒有了，但不代表我們11人都不在了，不知道該說些什麼安慰大家，就只是覺得抱歉，很抱歉，沒辦法報答你們給的愛，讓我更愧疚。」此話一出，全場爆哭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3866/d3866653.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3866%2Fd3866653.jpg&h=bfec7a28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Wanna One哭到跪在地上。（圖／翻攝自ollenTV）<br />\n<br />\n邕也是哭到泣不成聲，一直喊著「Wannable」，哽咽表示：「我不想一個人回家。」他回想起與成員度過的宿舍生活，大家一起打鬧、叫外賣，「但現在沒有人可以說了」。有開始就有離別，唱到最後一首歌時，姜丹尼爾再度開口：「真的要唱最後一首了，還是不要唱好了？你們知道我們在一起多久了嗎？539天，每天都很閃亮。」最後帶來歌曲《beautiful part 2》。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3866/d3866651.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3866%2Fd3866651.jpg&h=fdc97d55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲姜丹尼爾：「以後沒有Wanna One了，但不代表11人消失。」（圖／翻攝自ollenTV）<br />\n<br />\n最終說出感言時，朴佑鎮再度哭到無法說話，他緩過情緒後，擠出一句話說：「我真的不想跟大家分開。」但依舊在哭；朴志訓則是表示「這不是結束」，但他還是忍不住跪地大哭，金在奐用盡全力大喊3聲「Wannable」，最後姜丹尼爾原想要帶著笑臉離開，卻在最後一刻又低頭爆哭，坐著升降台離開舞台。<br />\n <br />\n除定褲睇新PRODUCE系列男團了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a04407697716083fd78bff05ab4626e6c1e2c8","tid":997822,"uid":223790,"like":242,"dislike":75,"score":167,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T12:58:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09c617d5b34579f7fcd578b7ccf2d461ea901f36","tid":997822,"uid":81725,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T12:59:05.000Z","msg":"咸咗出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb8ed4ad3d76961e17f4a0ec6fb2ea9bbfd766eb","tid":997822,"uid":223790,"like":47,"dislike":73,"score":-26,"ci